OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FShe has welcomed an increased
OL,8,Fawareness of the link between suicide
OL,9,Fand domestic abuse after a new study
OL,10,Fby Domestic Homicide Project shows a
OL,11,Frise in domestic abuse victims taking
OL,12,Ftheir own lives.
OL,14,FIn the 12 months to March 2025, 347
OL,15,Fdeaths were related to domestic abuse
OL,16,Fin England and Wales . This is an
OL,17,Fincrease of 85 from the previous year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
