OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FFor the first time suspected suicides
OL,8,Ffollowing domestic abuse have
OL,9,Fovertaken the number of homicide
OL,10,Fdeaths caused by domestic abuse.
OL,12,FDomestic Homicide Project suggests
OL,13,Fthis increase is largely down to a
OL,14,Fgreater awareness and a change in
OL,15,Fpolice practice which requires
OL,16,Fofficers to to check for a history of
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse at the scene of
OL,18,Fsuicides and unexpected deaths.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
