OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FIn 2011, Rachel Williams was shot in
OL,8,Fthe leg and severely injured by her ex-
OL,9,Fhusband whilst working at a
OL,10,Fhairdressers in Newport. He took his
OL,11,Fown life later that day. Shortly after
OL,12,Fthe attack, her son Jack also took his
OL,13,Fown life.
OL,15,F"I came out of hospital on Friday and
OL,16,Fsadly my 16-year-old son took his own
OL,17,Flife on the following Monday. This is
OL,18,Fall the result of one man's actions."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
