PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1777453579
OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,F"It's unbelievable, you wake up every
OL,8,Fday and think you're in a nightmare.
OL,9,FNot only having to deal with
OL,10,Feverything that happened with the
OL,11,Ftrauma of the shooting, but to lose my
OL,12,Fown son...You never get over it, you
OL,13,Fjust learn to live with it." Rachel
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
