OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FRachel believes Jack's suicide was a
OL,8,F'direct result' of the abuse she
OL,9,Fsuffered: "What these perpetrators put
OL,10,Fnot only the direct victim through,
OL,11,Fbut the children and anybody else in
OL,12,Fthe household through, is
OL,13,Funbelievable."
OL,15,F"I believe Jack died after everything
OL,16,Fthat happened. On their death
OL,17,Fcertificate... it should be suicide
OL,18,Ffrom domestic abuse."
OL,26,@qD@KOUzD@UO]
