OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FRachel has welcomed the increased
OL,8,Fawareness that suicide can be the
OL,9,Fresult of domestic abuse.
OL,11,F"It's great now that it's at the
OL,12,Fforefront of what's being talked about
OL,13,Fat the moment.
OL,15,F"If we do start recognising the link
OL,16,Fbetween suicide and domestic abuse,
OL,17,Fsociety will see the abuse as a bigger
OL,18,Fthreat to both life and society,"
OL,19,FRachel said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
