OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,FAssistant Commissioner Louisa Rolfe is
OL,8,Fthe national policing lead for
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse, she said: "This report
OL,10,Freflects important progress in how
OL,11,Fpolicing is identifying risk and
OL,12,Fpursuing justice in new ways.
OL,14,F"But these findings are also a stark
OL,15,Freminder that for too many victims,
OL,16,Fabuse was ongoing and already known
OL,17,Fbefore their death."
OL,19,FChief Executive of Advocacy After
OL,20,FFatal Domestic Abuse, Frank Mullane,
OL,21,Fsaid:
OL,26,@qD@[OUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
