OL,3,CAbuse survivor welcomes stronger
OL,4,Capproach in linking suicide to
OL,5,Cdomestic abuse
OL,7,F"For five years, AAFDA has been
OL,8,Fbringing families to meet police
OL,9,Fchiefs to share the weaknesses in
OL,10,Fpolice investigations. It has been
OL,11,Fheart warming to see those chiefs take
OL,12,Fthis so seriously and do something
OL,13,Fabout it.
OL,15,F"There are some excellent police
OL,16,Finvestigations after suicides which
OL,17,Ffollowed domestic abuse, but there are
OL,18,Fpoor ones too. Justice is scuppered
OL,19,Fwithout a professional and substantial
OL,20,Fpolice investigation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
